description:
Create the new typed Signature trait, FieldSpec, ConstraintSpec, and error types that replace the legacy MetaSignature.

**Files to create/modify:**
- crates/dspy-rs/src/core/signature.rs - new typed Signature trait + FieldSpec/ConstraintSpec
- crates/dspy-rs/src/core/errors.rs (NEW) - PredictError, ParseError, ConversionError hierarchy
- crates/dspy-rs/src/core/call_result.rs (NEW) - CallResult<O> with FieldMeta
- crates/dspy-rs/src/core/mod.rs - re-export new modules

**Search context (use morph):**
- Search 'MetaSignature' in dspy-rs to understand legacy trait
- Search 'FieldMeta' or 'field metadata' in baml-bridge for inspiration
- Search 'thiserror' in Cargo.toml to check if available
- Search 'ResponseCheck' in baml-types for constraint result patterns

**New types to define:**
```rust
pub struct FieldSpec {
    pub name: &'static str,       // LLM-facing name (alias or original)
    pub rust_name: &'static str,  // Rust field ident
    pub description: &'static str,
    pub type_ir: fn() -> TypeIR,
    pub constraints: &'static [ConstraintSpec],
}

pub trait Signature: Send + Sync + 'static {
    type Input: baml_bridge::BamlType;
    type Output: baml_bridge::BamlType;
    fn instruction() -> &'static str;
    fn input_fields() -> &'static [FieldSpec];
    fn output_fields() -> &'static [FieldSpec];
    fn output_format_content() -> &'static OutputFormatContent;
    fn from_parts(input: Self::Input, output: Self::Output) -> Self;
    fn into_parts(self) -> (Self::Input, Self::Output);
}
```
